HEADWORD: Candlewaster
<hw>Can"dle*wast`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
consumes candles by being up late for study or dissipation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A bookworm, a <qex>candlewaster</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>B.
Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

